From: UX Sync <ux-sync@landpage.dev>
Subject: [PATCH] fix(template-b): add feedback.js and formValidation.js to HTML pages

Add feedback.js and formValidation.js script tags before app.js in:
- index.html, menu.html, about.html, contact.html, gallery.html
These provide visual validation, shake animations, toast notifications, 
and skeleton loaders for UX improvements.

---
diff --git a/public/index.html b/public/index.html
index patched1..patched2 100644
--- a/public/index.html
+++ b/public/index.html
@@ -393,6 +393,8 @@
     <script src="/js/performance.js"></script>
     <script src="/js/mobile.js"></script>
     <script src="/js/a11y.js"></script>
+    <script src="/js/feedback.js"></script>
+    <script src="/js/formValidation.js"></script>
     <script src="/js/app.js"></script>
     <script src="/js/cart.js"></script>
     <script src="/js/whatsappFormatter.js"></script>
